## âš™ CI/CD Pipeline Stages

1. Clone source code from GitHub
2. Build Docker image
3. Push Docker image to DockerHub
4. Deploy Docker container on AWS EC2

---

## ğŸ§ª Jenkins Pipeline Flow

* SCM Checkout
