---

## ğŸ³ Docker Workflow

```bash
# Build Image
docker build -t devops-app .

# Tag Image
docker tag devops-app username/devops-app

# Push to DockerHub
docker push username/devops-app

# Run Container
docker run -d -p 80:80 username/devops-app
```

